# Google OAuth Client ID
# 1. Get your Client ID from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 2. Make sure to register ALL these Authorized JavaScript Origins:
#      http://localhost:5173          (npm run dev)
#      http://localhost:4173          (npm run preview)
#      https://tijara-eta.vercel.app  (production — update if your domain changes)
# 3. Copy this file to .env and fill in your value:
#      cp .env.example .env

VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
